OL,3,CMan arrested after bus driver slapped
OL,4,Cin face during road rage incident
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after he got
OL,7,Fon to a bus, slapped the driver across
OL,8,Fthe face before getting back off again.
OL,10,FThe incident, which is believed to be
OL,11,Fas a result of road rage, happened
OL,12,Faround 6.30pm on 5 April on Newhaven
OL,13,FRoad in Warrington.
OL,15,FThe driver of a Ford S-Max pulled up
OL,16,Falongside the bus as it came to a stop
OL,17,Fbefore opening the doors and boarding.
OL,19,Fsay the driver of the car, a 31-year-
OL,20,Fold local man, has since been arrested
OL,21,Fon suspicion of assault.
