OL,6,FHe remains in custody and is assisting
OL,7,Fofficers with their enquiries.
OL,9,FInspector Lee Hillyard said: "This
OL,10,Fbehaviour is abhorrent and completely
OL,11,Funacceptable, and I'm pleased that the
OL,12,Fperson responsible has been arrested.
OL,14,F"Bus drivers provide a public service
OL,15,Fto the communities in Warrington, and
OL,16,Fthey deserve to feel safe and
OL,17,Frespected while at work.
